videoSnippet.title: Vladimir Kramnik Loses to a Librarian
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Watch the interview with James Tarjan here https://www.chess.com/news/view/3-year-old-tarjan-beats-kramnik-in-battle-of-generations#comments

James Tarjan vs Vladimir Kramnik
Isle of Man Open (2017), Douglas ENG, rd 3, Sep-25 
Reti Opening: Anglo-Slav Variation. Torre System (A12)
